Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:08.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana has started to move, and it's \Nheading toward Wendy's guild, Caitshelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we faced off against \Nthe Poison Dragon, Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, doesn't old man \NJura kinda look like a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not a potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:55.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda... My body doesn't feel so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it his poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:05.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move... either...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus... I'm on transportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:21.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the pride of the Six \NGenerals, I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:27.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura, the Tenth Saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:44.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it... I can hear the end of the \Nlife of an Old Generation Dragon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Cobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, nothing more \Nthan a fake Dragon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for him as one of the six \Ngenerals that will crush the official guilds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted to hear the \Nvoice of my one friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cubellios...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you... his ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ally? I can gather as many as I wish shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using Nirvana's power, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call those allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Don't get testy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have taken an interest in your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you know what I mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you my first puppet slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:51.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with the stronger ideals will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Jura said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't wanna lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, then Father will abandon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:15.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Heaven's Eye can see through everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liquid Ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'm going to be abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... will abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:54.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be for the best, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, Oracion Seis will be no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause this is transportation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-dono, you are also unharmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Save Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Half of the Six Generals are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their stars have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I will create \Na new set of Generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Including this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:04.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this would happen eventually. \NFinally getting scouted by a Dark Guild, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu isn't gonna do what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana will soak this \Nboy's heart in darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and he will become nothing \Nbut my loyal servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that much strength left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He does not seem so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:36.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets extreme motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up... and beat... this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doin' it for you, but sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This city will shortly reach \Nits first destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will arrive at Caitshelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Wendy and Carla's guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:28.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your purpose. Why do \Nyou aim for Wendy-dono's guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ultra-inversion magic can change a \Nguild of light into one of darkness in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you'll see true hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let this guy off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard is gettin' to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:52.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:03.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no words for pitiful \Nweaklings like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become the judge ruling \Nover light and darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man needs to be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:15.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there is no talking with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:44.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:51.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand. I will not let you rest until you \Nsay why you are targeting Caitshelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, could this old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...be really crazy powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is someone with the title of \NWizard Saint, just like our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:39.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You surprised me for a moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:43.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the distinction of being one of \Nthe Wizard Saints is not just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many other guilds \Ncloser than Caitshelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some reason why \Nyou head there specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:03.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for those that \Nwill shortly be dead to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Rondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:28.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockiron Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:34.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's amazing! And \Nactually kinda scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:42.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand how \Nfutile this battle is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the reason you aim for Caitshelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what will you do if you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:55.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Capriccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rocks are bending!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Capriccio is a piercing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It will cut right through those damn rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rockiron Wall won't work against that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a way to pierce through,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:46.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but being able to dodge \Nit is impressive, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take back what you said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:59.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do, Wizard Saint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Capriccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockiron Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps that's what is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My Dark Capriccio will \Neventually turn you to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be good if it were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will finish this. And in a big way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Capriccio Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockiron Wall Continuous Chain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:45.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jura, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trapped in rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Supreme Rock Shatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:30.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even while withstanding such fierce attacks, he \Nnoticed he could use the shattered pieces of rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder even Lyon treats him with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:43.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! That guy's the \Nboss of Oracion Seis, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Tell me the reason you are \Naiming for Wendy-dono's guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, shouldn't we just stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it for me, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe that I... was... defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight... I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Six Generals will never be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the six prayers vanish,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"He?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey, didn't one of those symbols \Non his face just disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't freak me out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have nightmares about this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that all that \Nruckus was you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This city...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be heading toward our guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it. But don't worry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The snake charmer's defeated over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably Brain here that \Nwas manipulating Nirvana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:26.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So since we defeated him, \Nthe city should stop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:34.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we never found out why \Nhe was heading for Caitshelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there wasn't any \Nparticular reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the six prayers vanish,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,he will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:54.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some things left \Nunsolved, but it is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and stop this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:08.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The he-cat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...am dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are also dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dead of night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic cannot hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight isn't even injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've surpassed my father \Nas the strongest wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your face, one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five prayers have vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Midnight... Do not vanish, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is my prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that looks \Nlike controls at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how can we stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:33.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would stop \Nif we defeated Brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were naive! Now we have \Nno idea how to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:44.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I cast a spell \Nto cure poison, but he's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu can't handle transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So pitiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Motion sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:01.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a spell to cure his sense \Nof equilibrium will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Troia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm baaack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You rock, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me that magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sky Magic... That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:25.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't feel like transportation at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Lucy, summon a boat or train Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, this isn't the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get with the picture, would ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how to stop it. As \Nyou can see, there's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hot Eye... I mean, Richard, said that \Nthis was the place it was controlled from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:57.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe that Richard-dono would lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides having it stop or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,hasn't anyone noticed something \Neven more peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no controls, and no \None here in the King's Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain has been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So why is it still moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be operating on auto-pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:22.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana has already been set to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:37.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our... guild...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your guild ain't goin' anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do you this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:50.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana will not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you don't really bring the \N"gravitas" when you talk, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I say cool stuff all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:03.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:06.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh yeah, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:08.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "I'm all fired up!" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's do this!" Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your catch phrases!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: It is Your Words
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:20.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant words that people \Nremember in their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll kick your ass!" Yeah, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All people will remember \Nfrom that is the trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
